Victor Mohica https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Victor_Mohica 0 Victor Mohica (also known as Vic Mohica or Victor Mojica; born on July 31, 1933) is an American actor. His works include guest-star episode of Dark Shadows television series in 1969, featured actor in an episode of the Bearcats! television series in the fall of 1971, Little House on the Prairie Pilot Movie in 1974 and West Side Story Broadway version in 1968. His film credits include roles in Showdown (1973), Johnny Firecloud (1975), Victory at Entebbe (1976), Don't Answer the Phone (1980), The Final Countdown (1980), The Ghost Dance (1980) and Blood In Blood Out (1993).
